            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報25811點，升23點，較上日現貨收市價25774點高水37點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5496點，升4點，高水7點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報8927點，升7點，高水13點。</p>\n</div>",
