            "title": "中能控股供股截止 大股東按例以供股價1.57元提全購 股份今復牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中能控股(00228)公布供股結果，由於大股東及一致行動人士持股將由29.84%增至52.97%，將按例以供股價1.57元提全購。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中能控股官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/00228-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中能控股官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/00228-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中能控股官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上述作價較該股停牌前收迌價1.44元，有溢價約9.03%；較前60個交易日平均收市價1.37元，溢價達14.81%；較6月底止未經審核綜合資產淨值每股6.09元，則折讓74.22%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大股東表明，擬維持中能控股的上市地位，亦不會提高全面收購價。該股今日復牌。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15532465-%e4%b8%ad%e8%83%bd%e6%8e%a7%e8%82%a1%e4%be%9b%e8%82%a1%e6%88%aa%e6%ad%a2-%e5%a4%a7%e8%82%a1%e6%9d%b1%e6%8c%89%e4%be%8b%e4%bb%a5%e4%be%9b%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b91-57%e5%85%83%e6%8f%90%e5%85%a8%e8%b3%bc",
